
1. Server: apt install ./vernemq.....deb
3. Check service: systemctl status vernemq.service and systemctl restart vernemq.service

5. Generate pw
   => vmq-passwd -c /etc/vernemq/vmq.passwd xprojects # Here you have to enter the Password like xprojects
   - c  = create file, -u = update file and -d = delete user in filer

6. Check Config-File
   => nano /etc/vernemq/vernemq.con
10. generate an ACL-List
  => nano /etc/vernemq/vmq.acl
Here can you set the topic auths